                            <i class="lni lni-cogs"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="content">
                            <h3>Fast Setup</h3>
                            <p>
                                Ecom.io is easy to customize as per the need and developer friendly.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-8 col-sm-10">
                    <div class="single-feature">
                        <div class="icon">
                            <i class="lni lni-layout"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="content">
                            <h3>Clean Design</h3>
                            <p>
                                Want a responsive theme for your Ecommerce application? 
                                Looking for a customized Ecommerce website template?
                                We have a standard format too.
                            </p>
