                            <h2 class="mb-25 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                                Perfect Solution Thriving Online Business
                            </h2>
                            <p class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".4s">
                                We provide SaaS and Software on demand is a form of cloud service.
                                With a cloud-based solution, you do not need to be at a computer 
                                that has specific software installed. As long as you have access to 
                                the internet, you can use the SaaS service anywhere and anytime. It 
                                does not get easier than this!
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)"
                           class="main-btn btn-hover border-btn wow fadeInUp"
                           data-wow-delay=".6s">Discover More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- ======== about-section end ======== -->
    <!-- ======== about2-section start ======== -->
    <section id="about" class="about-section pt-150">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-6">
                    <div class="about-content">
                        <div class="section-title mb-30">
                            <h2 class="mb-25 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                                Easy to Use with Tons of Awesome Features
