                                    This template comes with 8 inner pages included 1 home page.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                        <div class="single-feature-extended">
                            <div class="icon">
                                <i class="lni lni-rocket"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">
                                <h3>Highly Optimized</h3>
                                <p>
                                    Search Engine Optimization (SEO) is one of the things 
